{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过实验，探究</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">二力平衡的条件。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">力能够改变物体的运动状态。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">二力平衡装置、钩码</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">把小车放在光滑的水平桌面上，向挂在小车两端的托盘里加砝码。观察小车在什么条件下会保持运动状态不变？</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Times-Roman\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">使两托盘里的砝码质量不相等；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Times-Roman\">2. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">使两托盘里的砝码质量相等；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Times-Roman\">3. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">保持两托盘里的砝码质量相等，把小车在水平桌面上扭转一个角度后释放；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:FZFSJW--GB1-0\">&hellip;&hellip;</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">请把实验条件和现象记录在表格中</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; font-family:Calibri; font-size:13px; width:564px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:360px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小车在水平方向所受二力的情况</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:203px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小车运动状态是否改变</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:98px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大小</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:90px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">方向</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:171px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是否在一条直线上</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:98px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不相等</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:90px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:171px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:203px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:98px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相等</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:90px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:171px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\