t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:203px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">作用在同一物体上的两个力，如果大小相等、方向相反，并且在同一条直线上，这两个力就彼此平衡。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.该实验过程利用了控制变量法；</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.平衡状态指静止或匀速直线运动状态；</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.二力平衡中两个力大小相等、方向相反、作用在同一物体上、作用在同一直线上；作用力与反作用力大小相等、方向相反、作用在相互作用的两个物体上、作用在同一直线上。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}